Why High Voltage best matches my tastes
- Instrumental focus and punch: The AC/DC High Voltage description emphasizes tight, blues‑based guitar riffs and punchy bass/drums with raw, guitar‑forward production. That directly matches my priority for punchy low end, crisp guitar tone and instrumental clarity that keeps rhythm and groove forward rather than burying it behind vocal smoothing.
